## **2. VANWINEFEST RECONNAISSANCE ACTIVITY SETS (UPDATED)**

### **Mapping Verchandising Framework to Reconnaissance Observations**

| Verchandising Motion | VanWineFest Reconnaissance Activity | Output | Feeds Into |
|----------------------|-------------------------------------|--------|------------|
| **Pre-Selection UI (Queue)** | **Observe queue pain points** - How long do guests wait? - What questions do they ask? - Do they abandon? | Field notes: "Queue anxiety patterns" | HOW-192 Pre-Selection UI design |
| **AR Infinite Shelf (DTC)** | **Document existing DTC attempts** - Do booths have QR codes for online stores? - What's the conversion pitch? | Photo documentation: "Existing QR codes at 10 booths" | HOW-192 Infinite Shelf UX |
| **AR Wayfinding (Crowd Flow)** | **Map crowd density zones** - Where do bottlenecks form? - Which booths get skipped? | GPS heatmap: "High-traffic vs. low-traffic zones" | Spatial Studio Place Packet spec |
| **Sponsored Canvas (Digital Real Estate)** | **Identify sponsor visibility opportunities** - Where do sponsors place banners? - Digital screens present? | Field notes: "Sponsor placement economics" | HOW-192 Sponsor integration |
| **Digital Tribes (Gamification)** | **Gauge social behavior patterns** - Do groups cluster by interest? - Do people share on social? | Field notes: "Observed tribal behaviors" | Digital Tribes design spec |
| **Story Flights (Micro-Bundles)** | **Observe tasting patterns** - Do guests ask for "intro flight"? - Do booths pre-bundle? | Field notes: "Flight offerings at 5 booths" | Vintage & Voice dialogue design |
| **Take-Home Kits (Deferred Fulfilment)** | **Document exit merchandising** - Do booths sell "festival packs"? - What's the pitch at checkout? | Photo: "Exit booth merchandising tactics" | HOW-192 deferred fulfilment spec |
| **Sponsor-Coached Micro-Classes** | **Attend seminars** - Are there paid mini-sessions? - What's the format? | Field notes: "Seminar economics + attendance" | Micro-class design for Wine Tycoon |
| **Digital Collectibles** | **Check for existing loyalty programs** - Do booths have stamp cards? - Any app-based rewards? | Field notes: "Loyalty mechanics observed" | Digital Tribes rewards system |
| **Sponsor Paths** | **Map themed routes** - Are there "Sparkling Circuit" or "Natural Wines" trails? - How are they marketed? | Field notes: "Route design + signage" | AR Wayfinding sponsored paths |
| **Festival Passports** | **Check for passport programs** - Physical cards? - Digital check-ins? | Field notes: "Passport mechanics + redemption rates" | Passport UX for future festivals |
| **At-Home Festival Extension** | **Document post-event offers** - Do organizers email follow-ups? - What's the content? | Screenshot: "Post-festival email campaigns" | At-home extension pack design |

